  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Enemies_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3f63dd2e5b3a9b64d93105ba50b014b3, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 73614639104
    m_Localized: A slow creature, so it doesn't pose much of a threat. However, its
      acidic physiology can cause serious damage if it comes into contact with its
      prey.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83978764288
    m_Localized: It seems that the viscous substance of its body is very sensitive
      to high temperatures.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6346391552
    m_Localized: Slimecat
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1205179138048
    m_Localized: Fleech
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1207590862848
    m_Localized: A flying annelid that feeds on the blood of other living beings.
      When hungry, it can quickly swoop down to bite its target.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1209830621184
    m_Localized: Due to its anatomy, constricting its body with the thorny vine seems
      to hurt it quite a bit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1255779221504
    m_Localized: Lupin Bandit (Claws)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1257989619712
    m_Localized: A member of the forest bandits. They were all affected by mutations
      that turned them into werewolves.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1260002885632
    m_Localized: Their werewolf abilities make them more resilient under the moonlight.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1317678759936
    m_Localized: Lupin Bandit (Shooter)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1319754940416
    m_Localized: Some of the forest bandits do not possess such powerful claws, but
      they compensate it with the ability to shoot teeth by opening their skull.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1321327804416
    m_Localized: At night, their shots are more deadly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1385718759424
    m_Localized: Shakira
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1387228708864
    m_Localized: The leader of the forest bandits. Her fierce personality and great
      strength have allowed her to remain the boss, standing up against all those
      who try to subdue her.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1388658966528
    m_Localized: '-'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1437086400512
    m_Localized: Yogui
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1438520852480
    m_Localized: An old lumberjack who has lived in the forest for a long time. He
      harbors a great resentment towards the roots of the great tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1439896584192
    m_Localized: '-'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
